**Testing checkpoint — Phase 3 done when:**
- [ ] Dashboard overview shows 4 KPIs with correct numbers
- [ ] Revenue chart renders with real transaction data
- [ ] Dark mode applies only to dashboard, not to other pages
- [ ] Date range filter updates all charts and KPIs
- [ ] Sales breakdown donut shows categories
- [ ] Purchase page shows per-supplier costs
- [ ] Profit page shows margin per product
- [ ] CSV export downloads valid file
- [ ] Mobile dashboard shows 2×2 KPI grid in light mode
- [ ] All dashboard pages load in < 2 seconds

**Common failure points:**
- Division by zero in profit margin — fix: guard with `NULLIF(cost, 0)` in SQL
- Chart renders with no data on new accounts — fix: show empty state component "No data yet — start logging transactions"
- Dark mode leaking to non-dashboard pages — fix: verify the `dark` class is only in the dashboard layout, not the root

