## Phase 5 — Polish, PWA & Launch (Weeks 10–12)

### Goal
Insights engine, PWA installability, landing page, performance optimization, security hardening, and production deployment.

---

### Week 10 — Insights Engine + PWA

**Files created — Insights:**

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/app/(app)/app/insights/page.tsx` | Full insight log with filters |
