### Week 12 — Testing, Security Hardening, Deploy

**Files created:**

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/lib/rateLimit.ts` | Token bucket rate limiter for AI endpoint |
| `src/components/ui/ErrorBoundary.tsx` | React error boundary |
| `src/components/ui/LoadingSkeleton.tsx` | Skeleton loaders per page type |
| `src/components/ui/EmptyState.tsx` | Empty state component |
| `src/app/not-found.tsx` | Custom 404 page |
| `src/app/error.tsx` | Custom error page |

**Rate limiting** on `/api/chat`: 20 requests per minute per user. Store counts in a simple in-memory Map (sufficient for Vercel serverless — resets on cold start, which is acceptable for v1). Use `X-RateLimit-Remaining` headers.

**Testing checklist** — see Part 8 (MVP Launch Checklist) for the complete list.

**Production deployment:**
1. Supabase: create production project, run all migrations, verify RLS
2. Vercel: connect GitHub repo, set env vars, deploy
3. DNS: point custom domain
4. SSL: automatic via Vercel
5. Monitoring: Vercel Analytics + Supabase Dashboard

**Testing checkpoint — Phase 5 done when:**
- [ ] Insights generate correctly (test each type manually)
- [ ] Cron endpoint produces insights batch
- [ ] Insights appear in chat stream via Realtime
- [ ] PWA installs on Android Chrome and iOS Safari
- [ ] Landing page renders on all breakpoints (320px → 1440px)
- [ ] All public pages load (pricing, terms, privacy)
- [ ] Rate limiter blocks excessive AI requests
- [ ] Error boundaries catch and display errors gracefully
- [ ] 404 page shows for invalid routes
- [ ] Production build (`npm run build`) completes without errors
- [ ] Lighthouse: Performance > 90, Accessibility > 95, SEO > 95
